2:T726,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is BrightEdge better than Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. BrightEdge scores 8.0 overall while Semrush scores 9.0. BrightEdge is best for Fortune 500 companies and enterprise marketing, while Semrush excels for SEO professionals and digital agencies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, BrightEdge or Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"BrightEdge starts at Custom and Semrush starts at $139.95/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from BrightEdge to Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both BrightEdge and Semrush support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about BrightEdge vs Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, BrightEdge holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10. Semrush has an overall rating of 9/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise BrightEdge for industry-leading enterprise seo platform and Semrush for most comprehensive seo toolkit available."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, BrightEdge or Semrush?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Semrush for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, BrightEdge remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize industry-leading enterprise seo platform. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}]