10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. BrightEdge is best suited for Fortune 500 companies, enterprise marketing, global SEO, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Semrush, meanwhile, shines for SEO professionals, digital agencies, marketing teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2007, BrightEdge describes itself as \"AI-powered enterprise SEO platform with real-time research and recommendations.\" Semrush, established in 2008, positions itself as \"All-in-one digital marketing toolkit with powerful SEO and competitive analysis.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Semrush** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (9.0 vs 8.0). However, this does not mean BrightEdge is a poor choice — far from it. BrightEdge excels in its own right, particularly for Fortune 500 companies and enterprise marketing.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value most comprehensive seo toolkit available, go with Semrush. If industry-leading enterprise seo platform matters more to you, BrightEdge is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
